\c 49
\s Jakove anoropafadza vanakomana vake
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jakove wakadana vanakomana vake, ndokuti\x + Det. 33.6-25.\x*: Unganai, kuti ndikuudzei zvichakuwirai mukupera kwemazuva\x + Num.. 24.14. Det. 4.30. Isa. 2.2. Jer. 23.20. Dhan. 2.28.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Unganai, munzwe \add imwi\add* vanakomana vaJakove, muteerere kuna Israeri baba venyu.
\p
\v 3 Rubheni, uri dangwe rangu\x + 29.32.\x*, simba rangu, nekutanga kwesimba\x + Det. 21.17. Map. 78.51; 105.36.\x* rangu; kukwana kwerukudzo\x + 4.7.\x*, nekukwana kwesimba.
\v 4 Unotutuma semvura, haungavi wakakwana; nokuti wakakwira kuuvato hwababa vako\x + 35.22. 1 Makor. 5.1.\x* ndokusvibisa; wakakwira kumubhedha wangu.
\p
\v 5 Simioni naRevhi vana vamai vamwe\x + 29.33,34.\x*; zvombo zvavo inhumbi dzekupamba.
\v 6 Mweya wangu ngaurege kupinda pakurangana kwavo. Rukudzo\x + Zvir. 11.13; 20.19.\x* rwangu ngarwurege kusanganiswa neungano yavo\x + Map. 16.9; 57.8.\x*; nokuti pakutsamwa kwavo vakauraya munhu, uye nekuzvifadza vakagura nzombe marunda.
\v 7 Kutsamwa kwavo ngakutukwe, nokuti kwakasimba; nehasha dzavo, nokuti dzaiva dzine utsinye; ndichavaparadzanisa muna Jakove\x + Num.. 3.6. Josh. 19.1. 1 Makor. 4.27.\x*, nekuvaparadzira muna Israeri.
\p
\v 8 Judha, iwe vana vababa vako vachakurumbidza\x + 29.35; 27.29.\x*; ruoko rwako ruchava pamutsipa wevavengi vako; vanakomana\x + 2 Zvak. 22.41.\x* vababa vako vachakukotamira\x + 1 Makor. 5.2.\x*.
\v 9 Judha imbwanana yeshumba; iwe\x + Det. 33.22.\x* wakwira paudzimba, mwanakomana wangu. Wakakotama, wakazvambarara seshumba, uye seshumbakadzi; ndiani achamusimudza\x + Num.. 23.24; 24.9. Zvak. 5.5.\x*?
\v 10 Tsvimbo yeushe haingabvi kuna\x + Num.. 24.17. Zek. 10.11.\x* Judha, nemupi wemurairo kubva pakati\x + Map. 60.7; 108.8. Det. 28.57.\x* petsoka dzake, kusvika Shiro asvika; uye ndudzi dzichamuteerera iye\x + Zvir. 30.17.\x*.
\v 11 Unosungira mbongoro yake pamuzambiringa, nemwana\x + 2 Madz. 18.32. Isa. 5.2. Jer. 2.21. Vato. 16.4. Num.. 13.23.\x* wembongorohadzi yake pamuzambiringa wakanaka. Wakasuka nguvo dzake muwaini, nechekupfeka chake muropa remazambiringa.
\v 12 Meso \add ake\add* achatsvuka newaini, uye\x + Zvir. 23.29.\x* meno \add ake\add* achachena nemukaka.
\p
\v 13 Zebhuruni achagara pamahombekombe\x + Det. 33.18,19. Josh. 19.10,11.\x* egungwa\x + Det. 1.7. Josh. 9.1. Vato. 5.17.\x*; uye achava panomira zvikepe; nemuganhu wake uchasvika paSidhoni.
\p
\v 14 Isasikari imbongoro ine simba, inorara pasi pakati pemitoro miviri\x + Vato. 5.16. Map. 68.13. Vato. 5.15. 1 Makor. 12.32.\x*.
\v 15 Zvino wakaona zororo kuti rakanaka, nenyika kuti inofadza, akarerekera fudzi rake\x + 1 Zvak. 10.9.\x* kuti atakure, akava muranda wechibharo\x + Eki. 1.11. Josh. 16.10.\x*.
\p
\v 16 Dhani achatonga vanhu vake\x + Gen.. 30.6.\x*, serumwe rwemarudzi aIsraeri.
\v 17 Dhani achava nyoka panzira, mvumbi mugwara, inoruma zvitsitsinho zvebhiza kuti mutasvi waro awire shure.
\v 18 Ndakamirira ruponeso\x + Map. 25.5. Isa. 25.9.\x* rwenyu, Jehovha.
\p
\v 19 Gadhi, hondo ichamuvamba\x + Gen.. 30.11.\x*, asi iye achavamba pazvitsitsinho.
\p
\v 20 Kubva kuna Asheri, kudya kwake kuchakora; iye achauya nezvinonaka zvemadzishe.
\p
\v 21 Nafutari inondo hadzi yakasunungurwa, anobudisa mashoko akanaka.
\p
\v 22 Josefa idavi rinobereka, idavi rinobereka patsime; matavi anokwira pamusoro pemadziro.
\v 23 Vanopfura neuta\x + 37.19.\x* vakamubata zvinorwadza\x + 37.24,28; 39.20.\x*, vaka\add mu\add*pfura, vakamuvenga\x + 27.41; 50.15.\x*\x + Map. 18.14.\x*.
\v 24 Asi uta hwake hwakaramba\x + Job. 29.20.\x* hwakasimba, nemaoko ezvanza zvake akasimbiswa nemaoko eWemasimba waJakove\x + Map. 132.2,5. Isa. 1.24.\x*; anobva ikoko Mufudzi, ibwe raIsraeri\x + Map. 80.1. Isa. 28.16. 1 Pet. 2.4.\x*;
\v 25 naMwari wababa vako achakubatsira\x + 35.3; 50.17; 17.1.\x*, uye neWemasimbaose achakuropafadza nemaropafadzo ematenga anobva kumusoro, maropafadzo ekudzika kurere pasi, maropafadzo emazamu neechizvaro.
\v 26 Maropafadzo ababa vako anopfuura maropafadzo emateteguru angu, kusvika pamiganhu pemakomo asingaperi\x + Det. 33.15. Habh. 3.6.\x*; achava pamusoro waJosefa, nepanhongonya\x + Det. 33.16.\x* yewakaparadzaniswa kuvana vababa vake.
\p
\v 27 Bhenjamini ibere rinobvamburanya\x + Eze. 22.27.\x*; mangwanani achadya chakajimbiwa, uye madekwani achagovanisa chakapambiwa\x + Zek. 14.1. Eze. 39.10.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Ava vese ndiwo marudzi ane gumi nemaviri aIsraeri; ndizvo zvakataura baba vavo kwavari, ndokuvaropafadza; vakaropafadza umwe neumwe nekuropafadzwa kwake.
\v 29 Zvino wakavaraira ndokuti kwavari: Ini ndobva ndounganidzwa kuvanhu vangu\x + 49.33; 25.8.\x*; munondiviga kune madzibaba\x + 47.30.\x* angu, mubako riri mumunda waEfuroni, muHeti\x + 23.9; 50.13.\x*,
\v 30 mubako riri mumunda weMakipera, riri pakatarisana neMamure, panyika yeKenani, riya Abhurahama raakatenga pamwe nemunda kuna Efuroni, muHeti\x + 23.16,17.\x*, kuti zvive zvake zvepekuvigira;
\v 31 ndipo pavakaviga Abhurahama naSara mukadzi wake\x + 23.19; 25.9.\x*; ndipo pavakaviga Isaka\x + 35.29.\x* naRabheka mukadzi wake; ndipo pandakaviga Rea;
\v 32 munda uya nebako riri mauri, zvakatengwa kuvana vaHeti.
\v 33 Zvino Jakove wakati apedza kuraira vanakomana vake, akapeta tsoka dzake pamubhedha, mweya wake ukabuda, akaunganidzwa kuvanhu vake\x + 49.29.\x*.